{"tid":2245524,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港寬頻為跑數連阿婆都呃","createTime":"2020-10-16T09:45:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-16T10:40:59.000Z","uid":227419,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"bc7332504bb042bc8ad6b46f7d73ce6197d91f2b","tid":2245524,"uid":227419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T09:45:06.000Z","msg":"專注服務弱勢社群的「維修香港」義工團隊，昨（15 日）晚在 Facebook 透露，在一次探訪長者的過程當中，發現該名長者在家中安裝了香港寬頻的寬頻上網服務，每月要交逾 200 元月費，另加每月 35 元的實體帳單手續費，然而該長者卻從來不上網。「維修香港」義工質疑，香港寬頻職員是否為了「跑數」，連長者都不放過。<br />\n香港寬頻的官方 Facebook 帳戶今日凌晨在「維修香港」相關帖文留言，表示已經發電郵給「維修香港」，希望了解更多詳情 ...<br />\n<br />\n立場新聞：<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E7%BE%A9%E5%B7%A5%E6%8E%A2%E5%85%AB%E6%97%AC%E4%BC%AF%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BE%E5%AE%B6%E4%B8%AD%E8%A3%9D%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%AF%AC%E9%A0%BB-%E9%95%B7%E8%80%85%E4%B8%8D%E8%AB%B3%E4%B8%8A%E7%B6%B2-%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E9%8A%B7%E5%94%AE%E5%93%A1%E7%82%BA-%E8%B7%91%E6%95%B8-%E7%A1%AC%E9%8A%B7/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E7%25BE%25A9%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E6%258E%25A2%25E5%2585%25AB%25E6%2597%25AC%25E4%25BC%25AF%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%258F%25BE%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%25A3%259D%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25AF%25AC%25E9%25A0%25BB-%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%2580%2585%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25AB%25B3%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%25B6%25B2-%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591%25E9%258A%25B7%25E5%2594%25AE%25E5%2593%25A1%25E7%2582%25BA-%25E8%25B7%2591%25E6%2595%25B8-%25E7%25A1%25AC%25E9%258A%25B7%2F&d=Z58AETknIeTPCCdXMCOVUwsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=71712e64\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E7%25BE%25A9%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E6%258E%25A2%25E5%2585%25AB%25E6%2597%25AC%25E4%25BC%25AF%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%258F%25BE%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%25A3%259D%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25AF%25AC%25E9%25A0%25BB-%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%2580%2585%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25AB%25B3%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%25B6%25B2-%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E